Software requirements:

It is needed to install the following software:

sudo easy_install pathtools
sudo easy_install distribute
sudo easy_install psycopg2
sudo easy_install select_backport
sudo easy_install argh
sudo easy_install argcomplete	
sudo easy_install -m matplotlib
sudo easy_install libyaml OR sudo easy_install pyyaml
sudo easy_install brew
sudo easy_install cherrypy
sudo easy_install watchdog (Install FSevents to handle all the file events using this handler instead of Kqueue)


Frequent Questions:

Error: pg_config executable not found.

Please add the directory containing pg_config to the PATH
or specify the full executable path with the option:

    python setup.py build_ext --pg-config /path/to/pg_config build ...

SOLUTION: PATH=$PATH:/Library/Postgres/9.3/bin


Command to run the system:
/usr/local/watchmedo/watchmedo log --patterns="*.*" --recursive /Users/hector